        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fairness in Firearm Testing Act</b> </p> <p>This bill establishes additional requirements for the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives (ATF). </p> <p>Specifically, the bill requires the ATF to make a video recording of its process for evaluating and testing an item to determine if it is a firearm or ammunition. </p>]]>
        </text>
